This package contains classes of the runtime layer.

Class Summary
AbstractBo2RuntimeCmd AbstractBo2RuntimeCmd is an RuntimeCommand that can be implemented without defining an Operation.

EntitiesQueryCmd<Q extends EntitiesQuery<P>,P> A command that encapsulates an EntitiesQuery.
Launcher Deprecated. use MultiLauncher instead
MultiLauncher The MultiLauncher's responsibility is to execute multiple RuntimeCommand.
NamedResourceWrapperManager Named manager of ResourceWrapper objects.
ProviderImpl Base implementation of Provider.
PwCrudCmd<P extends PersistentObject<?>> PwCrudCmd is a CrudCmd that operates on a PersistentObject using a PersistenceWorker that is created by the Factory.
RuntimeCommand RuntimeCommand is a runtime layer object that provides a transaction context to a sequence of operations and executes them.
SimpleBo2RuntimeCmd Deprecated. Use AbstractRuntimeCommand.
TransactionExecution  
UnitTestCmd<T> UnitTestCmd is a runtime command developed for writing unit tests.
 

Package gr.interamerican.bo2.impl.open.runtime Description

This package contains classes of the runtime layer. The classes of this package are used by specific runtime implementations.
